<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recolon - Meet, Share and Mentor</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favicon_io/favicon-32x32.png">

    <!--CSS ANIMATE-ON-SCROLL Library-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css"/>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/semantic-ui/2.4.1/semantic.min.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/media-query.css">

    
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <nav class="ui fixed menu">

    <div style="margin: 5px 0 0 10%; cursor: pointer;" class="item">
       <i style="color: #0070ba;" class="edit outline icon"></i> <a style="font-size: 22.5px; font-weight: 700; color: #0070ba;" href="#">Recolon</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 8px 0 0 5%;" class="item">
      <a style="font-size: 15px; color: #424242; font-weight: 700; padding: 0 15px;" href="#">About <i style="font-size: 12px;" class="chevron down icon"></i></a>
      <a style="font-size: 15px; color: #424242; font-weight: 700; padding: 0 15px;" href="#">Contact</a>
      <a style="font-size: 15px; color: #424242; font-weight: 700; padding: 0 15px;" href="#">Find a mentor</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;" class="right menu">
        <a style="color: #0070ba; font-size: 15px;" href="/recolon/accounts/register" class="item"><i class="pencil alternate icon"></i>Register</a>
        <a style="color: #0070ba; font-size: 15px;" href="/recolon/accounts/login" class="item"><i class="user icon"></i>Login</a>
    </div>

</nav><hr>
</header>




<!--Error message -->
<% if(error && error.length > 0) { %>
    <div class="ui red message">
      <%= error %> 
    </div>  
  <% }%> 
  
  <!--Success message-->
  

<section class="page-highlight">
  <div class="highlight">
    <h2>Share ideas and discuss tech with other developers</h2>
    <p>Recolon is a developer-first, content-driven platform.<br> Share ideas, Build Cool Stuff and Mentor Juniors</p>
    <button class="ui blue button" ><a href="/recolon/accounts/register">Get Started For Free</a><i id="arrow-right" class="arrow alternate circle right outline icon"></i></button>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="info">
  <div class="card-boxes">

    <div class="card-box">
      <img src="/svgs/svg-6.svg" alt="">
      <h3>Share Ideas</h3>
      <p>Through the contents you write, meet other developers who are interested in the same niche as you and share ideas.</p>
      <i class="arrow alternate circle right outline icon arrow-right"></i>
    </div>

    <div class="card-box">
      <img src="/svgs/svg-8.svg" alt="">
      <h3>Build Together</h3>
      <p>By meeting other developers, it gives an opportunity to collaborate with them and build your next awesome software together.</p>
      <i class="arrow alternate circle right outline icon arrow-right"></i>
    </div>

    <div class="card-box">
      <img src="/svgs/svg-9.svg" alt="">
      <h3>Become a mentor</h3>
      <p>Development is hard enough when you can't find a mentor. Help junior developers grow by mentoring them through their journey.</p>
      <i class="arrow alternate circle right outline icon arrow-right"></i>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>

<section class="dev-community-section">
  <div class="d-comm">
    <h2>Join a community. Write your stuff. Share your ideas.<br> And so much more.</h2>
    <p>Peruse the entire developer community and find what's right for you.</p>
    <p>All on <i class="edit outline icon"></i>Recolon</p>
    <button class="ui blue button"><a style="font-size: 16.5px; color: #fdfdfd; text-decoration: none;" href="#">See all Community</a> <i class="chevron right icon"></i></button>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="showing-dev-community">
  <div class="show-info">
    <h1 style="font-size: 36px; color: #fdfdfd; line-height: 50px;">Write Simply.</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #fdfdfd;">Check out these awesome communities.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="show-dev-comm-container">

    <div class="comm-cards">
      <div id="comm-card1" class="comm-card">
          <p>Programming</p>
      </div>
      
      <div id="comm-card2" class="comm-card">
        <p>Web Development</p>
      </div>
      
      <div id="comm-card3" class="comm-card">
        <p>Dev Ops</p>
      </div>
      
      <div id="comm-card4" class="comm-card">
        <p>Software Engineering</p>
      </div>
      
      <div id="comm-card5" class="comm-card">
        <p>Machine Learning</p>
      </div>
      
      <div id="comm-card6" class="comm-card">
        <p>Data Science</p>
      </div>

      <div id="comm-card7" class="comm-card">
        <p>Cloud Computing</p>
      </div>

      <div id="comm-card8" class="comm-card">
        <p>Cyber Security</p>
      </div>

      <div id="comm-card9" class="comm-card">
        <p>Testing</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

  <!--Javascript animate-on-scroll library-->
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.js"></script>
  <script>
      AOS.init({
          offset: 400,
          duration: 1200
      });
  </script>


  <!--JQUERY Plugin-->
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <!--Custom Script-->
  <script src="/javascript/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>